data.description: You will love this beautifully updated and well maintained brick rancher on almost half acre lot, 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths with 2 master suites, many updates include remodeled main master bath with large ceramic tiled shower, remodeled hall bathroom, hot water heater and dishwasher 2021, updated plumbing. 16 x 24 shed with loft and power. 8 x 8 plastic shed, fresh paint, plenty of space to add a carport or garage. Purchaser to verify all information. Call today to view this lovely home.
